{"id":10972,"date":"2024-01-09T08:20:48","date_gmt":"2024-01-09T08:20:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.screeningdate.com\/?p=10972"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:22:58","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:22:58","slug":"sprott-shaw-college-application","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/","title":{"rendered":"Sprott Shaw College Application 2024 &#8211; Apply Now"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Want to study at Vancouver, Sprott Shaw College application 2024 is now open for both domestic and International Students. Sprott Shaw College is competitive and also consider early application. This is Vancouver &#8211; a jewel of Canada<\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_64 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#How_to_Apply_Sprott_Shaw_College\" title=\"How to Apply | Sprott Shaw College\">How to Apply | Sprott Shaw College<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#Find_a_Program\" title=\"Find a Program\">Find a Program<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#Check_the_Requirements\" title=\"Check the Requirements\">Check the Requirements<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#Apply_Online\" title=\"Apply Online\">Apply Online<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#Receive_Offer_of_Admission\" title=\"Receive Offer of Admission\">Receive Offer of Admission<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#Pay_Your_Tuition_Deposit\" title=\"Pay Your Tuition Deposit \">Pay Your Tuition Deposit <\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#Wait_for_Your_Online_Contract\" title=\"Wait for Your Online Contract \">Wait for Your Online Contract <\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application\/#Acceptance_Letter\" title=\"Acceptance Letter\">Acceptance Letter<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>visit this link to watch application steps. https:\/\/youtu.be\/a4d5CbK0b3A<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"how-to-apply-sprott-shaw-college\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_Sprott_Shaw_College\"><\/span>How to Apply | Sprott Shaw College<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Apply to Sprott Shaw College in Seven (7) Steps<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"find-a-program\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Find_a_Program\"><\/span><strong>Find a Program<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">At Sprott Shaw College, we offer over 130 practical courses in a wide range of fields, including healthcare, business, administration, childcare, community service, trades, design, and more. Here, select a program that interests you.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"check-the-requirements\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Check_the_Requirements\"><\/span><strong>Check the Requirements<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Check the Admission Requirements for international students to apply for admission here.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"nitro-offscreen\">\n<h4 id=\"apply-online\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Apply_Online\"><\/span><strong>Apply Online<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>When your admission requirement is complete, you can Fill out the application form to apply to Sprott Shaw College <a href=\"https:\/\/sprottshaw.com\/international-application-form\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p class=\"nitro-offscreen\"><strong><em>Ensure you have all required documents, including:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ol class=\"nitro-offscreen\">\n<li><strong><em>A copy of your valid Passport<\/em><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><em>A copy of your high school\/post-secondary transcript<\/em><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><em>A copy of your valid study permit (if applicable)<\/em><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><em>Proof of English proficiency such as IELTS or TOEFL scores (if available)<\/em><\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong><em>A non-refundable application fee of $350 CAD<\/em><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"receive-offer-of-admission\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Receive_Offer_of_Admission\"><\/span><strong>Receive Offer of Admission<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>After your application has been reviewed and accepted, you will get an invoice or a Conditional <a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-check-sprottshaw-admission-status\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Letter of Offer<\/a>.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"pay-your-tuition-deposit\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Pay_Your_Tuition_Deposit\"><\/span><strong>Pay Your Tuition Deposit <\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Pay your tuition deposit. Cash, check, credit card, e-transfer, bank draft, and\/or wire transfer are all options for making payments. To confirm and reserve your spot, a tuition deposit is required.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"wait-for-your-online-contract\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wait_for_Your_Online_Contract\"><\/span><strong>Wait for Your Online Contract <\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>An official contract will be issued online once the tuition deposit has been received. Please return the contract and sign it. Please watch the video below for more information on how to sign a document online.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"acceptance-letter\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Acceptance_Letter\"><\/span><strong>Acceptance Letter<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Once\u00a0the\u00a0signed\u00a0contracts\u00a0have\u00a0been\u00a0received,\u00a0you\u00a0will\u00a0receive\u00a0an\u00a0official letter\u00a0of\u00a0acceptance\u00a0via\u00a0email.<\/p>\n<p>Ready to start application process? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/sprott-shaw-college-application-form\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Want to study at Vancouver, Sprott Shaw College application 2024 is now open for both domestic and International&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[838],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10972"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=10972"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10972\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":18455,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10972\/revisions\/18455"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=10972"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=10972"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=10972"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}